{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":102,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-31T12:03:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any way we could bring back the old color palate? This most recent update has changed the colors! Yes, I know there\u0027s the \u0022more colors\u0022 option at the bottom, but the older one was much more convenient... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI promise that\u0027s my only gripe of the day! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-31T20:20:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean the options for text color and background? If so, click on those edit buttons and then \u0022more colors.\u0022 \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#003366;\u0022\u003EYo\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#00cc99;\u0022\u003Eu wi\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#660000;\u0022\u003Ell \u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ff33cc;\u0022\u003Efi\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ff33cc;\u0022\u003End a\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#00cccc;\u0022\u003E rainb\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffff00;\u0022\u003Eow se\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#00cc00;\u0022\u003Electi\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#993300;\u0022\u003Eon of hues!\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","Crea